-- Poland's PPG scraps guidance, mulls Russia project sale 
-- By Wiktor Szary
-- Mon Aug 18, 2014 05:13AM EDT
-- None



WARSAW, Aug 18 (Reuters) - Polish developer Platinum Properties Group (PPG) <PPGP.WA> cancelled its earnings forecasts for this and next year and said it might sell its Moscow project, as political tensions between Russia and Ukraine cast clouds over its Russian business.

